title: CALL & SEE 4 YOURSELF! > Historic Upscale Neighborhood & Awesome Amens
posting_body: ['Enjoy The Good Life...', 'Welcome Home!', 'Seize your chance to live in The Irvington, one of the most iconic apartment communities in Portland, OR.', 'The Irvington', 'show contact info', '1532 NE 21st Avenue', 'Portland OR 97232', 'Bed: 1', 'Bath: 1', 'Rent: 1599', 'The Irvington offers something for everyone.', 'See our available amenities to find something that speaks to The Pearl District.', 'We offer our residents a myriad of top-notch amenities to make life that much easier so that you have more time to kick back.', 'Our Walk Score of 87 makes us as a “Very with roomy one-bedroom apartment floor plans with modern design and filled with closets, so you can find the home that fits your lifestyle for years to come.', 'Got some downtime and need to unwind?', 'If you want somewhere serene to clear your head, you need look no further than our smoke-free community with long private balconies, gated off-street parking, free bike storage, and parcel lockers.']
